  1394→
  1395→IMPORTANT RULES:
  1396→- Be SPECIFIC. Quote their actual words. Reference real answers, not generic advice.
  1397→- For filler_words: estimate counts based on patterns you see in their text (hedge words, qualifiers like "I think", "kind of", "sort of", "you know", etc.)
